It's not that.
My back muscles are...

01:00:07.377 --> 01:00:09.411
Oh, come on, you know
that's bullshit!

01:00:09.413 --> 01:00:10.779
May I make
a suggestion?

01:00:32.502 --> 01:00:33.503
You know...

01:00:35.538 --> 01:00:37.438
I hate to give
the kid credit, but...

01:00:37.440 --> 01:00:39.641
I know, I know,
who'd have thunk?

01:00:39.643 --> 01:00:41.809
- Hey, fellas.
- Hello, ladies.

01:00:41.811 --> 01:00:44.411
