boyfriend tonight?

01:02:24.714 --> 01:02:26.950
He's downstairs.

01:02:28.485 --> 01:02:29.620
I'm just kidding.

01:02:31.788 --> 01:02:35.623
Guys are a little
taken back

01:02:35.625 --> 01:02:36.991
