01:03:13.830 --> 01:03:14.965
Oh, yeah.

01:03:37.686 --> 01:03:39.654
Oh, shit.

01:03:39.656 --> 01:03:41.021
Morning, Pinky Lee.

01:03:41.023 --> 01:03:43.056
Have you seen John?

01:03:43.058 --> 01:03:44.759
