were so little.

01:04:35.645 --> 01:04:37.645
I don't want you
to worry.

01:04:37.647 --> 01:04:41.049
You know, everything is
gonna be good for us.

01:04:41.051 --> 01:04:42.851
You'll see.

01:04:42.853 --> 01:04:44.751
I promise.

01:04:44.753 --> 01:04:46.020
